text:
Always a great time at UnWine & Whiskey Bar 放松吧!

The atmosphere is cozy and relaxed, making it a perfect spot to unwind after a long day. They have a good decent selection of wines and whiskeys, catering to both casual drinkers and connoisseurs.

The staff is friendly and knowledgeable, always ready to recommend a good drink based on your preferences. The music and lighting set the right mood without being too loud or overwhelming.

A hidden gem worth visiting for a chill night out!
Great place to relax with friends or on a date. Cozy ambience, excellent whiskey, beer and wine selection. The staff is friendly and knows their stuff well. Will definitely return!
Walking in, I instantly felt welcomed. The environment resembles a cozy living room, with sofa and comfortable pillows for you to hug on while sipping on your drink.
Cozy, welcoming pub with lively atmosphere, friendly lady boss, and comfortable seating. Perfect for relaxing and hanging out with friends. Highly recommend this new spot for a good time.

Came recently to unwind & soak in the atmosphere.
The service was good, nice music with great ambience
Paired with yummy satay  from next door restaurant
A good cozy place to chill after a day of hard work
